1
00:01:09,820 --> 00:01:13,500
=Inherently Kind=

2
00:01:14,780 --> 00:01:17,700
=Episode 9=
(Memory Regained)

3
00:01:28,280 --> 00:01:28,879
Let me go!

4
00:01:30,439 --> 00:01:31,079
Master,

5
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:33,319
please drive out the evil spirit.

6
00:01:33,439 --> 00:01:36,359
This demon does have some skill.

7
00:01:37,319 --> 00:01:38,000
It doesn't matter.

8
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:41,519
I will subdue it.

9
00:01:49,879 --> 00:01:51,000
Amitabha.

10
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:53,719
As urgent as the law decrees.

11
00:01:53,959 --> 00:01:55,400
By the command of the celestial law,

12
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:57,519
summon the divine power.

13
00:02:01,959 --> 00:02:03,079
Is this the Dark Ages?

14
00:02:03,560 --> 00:02:05,159
You're still with the superstitions?

15
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:06,599
Did your brains take a hit?

16
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:09,479
Master,

17
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:12,039
it's my sister-in-law's body after all.

18
00:02:12,199 --> 00:02:13,400
Please don't hurt her.

19
00:02:13,520 --> 00:02:14,520
Maybe I could do it instead.

20
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:16,719
Then I will leave it to you.

21
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:17,599
Alright.

22
00:02:31,639 --> 00:02:33,439
Mr. Mu, Gu Qingmei is in danger!

23
00:02:40,240 --> 00:02:40,800
One.

24
00:02:45,719 --> 00:02:46,240
Two.

25
00:02:48,039 --> 00:02:49,000
You are still counting?

26
00:02:49,560 --> 00:02:50,840
Then keep counting.

27
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:51,800
Three.

28
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:52,840
Four.

29
00:02:56,159 --> 00:02:57,439
Insolent demon!

30
00:02:58,080 --> 00:02:59,120
So you are the master.

31
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:02,319
I am the insolent demon,

32
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:04,000
and you are here to uphold justice?

33
00:03:04,759 --> 00:03:05,400
I was wrong.

34
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:07,439
I am just a servant.

35
00:03:07,879 --> 00:03:09,360
I am not a master.

36
00:03:09,599 --> 00:03:10,520
Please spare me!

37
00:03:10,639 --> 00:03:11,520
It's...

38
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:12,360
It was her.

39
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:14,159
She sent me.

40
00:03:14,639 --> 00:03:15,960
Oh my goodness!

41
00:03:21,199 --> 00:03:21,719
It wasn't me!

42
00:03:22,159 --> 00:03:22,639
It wasn't me!

43
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:26,159
It wasn't me!

44
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:28,360
It wasn't me!

45
00:03:28,479 --> 00:03:29,080
Four times.

46
00:03:29,639 --> 00:03:30,800
I am returning the favor.

47
00:03:31,439 --> 00:03:31,960
One.

48
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:32,759
I did not do it.

49
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:33,400
Two.

50
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:34,280
Three.

51
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:35,280
Four.

52
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:46,879
Mom.

53
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:53,639
(It is all my fault.)

54
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:55,920
(I knew you're not Gu Qingmei,)

55
00:04:56,879 --> 00:04:58,519
(yet I still left you alone there.)

56
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:00,839
(I should have taken you away.)

57
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:15,079
(You talk too much.)

58
00:05:15,199 --> 00:05:16,360
(Are you even a man?)

59
00:06:53,839 --> 00:06:54,439
(Assistant Tang!)

60
00:06:57,439 --> 00:06:58,079
(Good morning, boss.)

61
00:06:58,439 --> 00:06:59,199
(Find her.)

62
00:07:00,959 --> 00:07:01,759
(Find who?)

63
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:03,600
(The woman from last night.)

64
00:07:05,199 --> 00:07:06,279
(Alright, I'll go find her right away.)

65
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:10,120
(Hurry up!)

66
00:07:10,839 --> 00:07:11,399
(Money-grubber.)

67
00:07:11,439 --> 00:07:12,399
(I'm going to find her now!)

68
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:28,360
I have been looking for you for so long.

69
00:07:30,439 --> 00:07:31,879
And here you are.

70
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:35,680
As long as you wake up safely,

71
00:07:38,079 --> 00:07:40,040
I will not let you go this time.

72
00:07:57,959 --> 00:07:58,800
(Take this USB drive.)

73
00:07:59,439 --> 00:08:00,360
(Is it Meiyan International?)

74
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:01,480
(They are trying to stop you
from exposing them.)

75
00:08:03,199 --> 00:08:03,839
(Let go!)

76
00:08:26,759 --> 00:08:27,360
Thank goodness!

77
00:08:28,079 --> 00:08:28,800
You are awake.

78
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:31,079
Mr. He.

79
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:33,000
Tian Gang was almost killed tonight.

80
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:34,639
We don't know who did it.

81
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:36,399
Find out as soon as possible

82
00:08:36,559 --> 00:08:38,200
who sent the attacker tonight.

83
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:39,799
Could what Tian Gang has

84
00:08:40,519 --> 00:08:41,919
be harmful to our company?

85
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:46,039
No matter what he has,

86
00:08:46,600 --> 00:08:48,720
find a way to take him away.

87
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:57,879
Has everything come back to you?

88
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:03,000
Did you know my identity all this time?

89
00:09:03,559 --> 00:09:05,039
You knew I was not Gu Qingmei.

90
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:07,679
You belong to me.

91
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:09,600
I could never mistake you.

92
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:12,759
Who says I belong to you?

93
00:09:13,679 --> 00:09:14,559
Just that night.

94
00:09:21,639 --> 00:09:22,519
Then from now on,

95
00:09:23,639 --> 00:09:24,399
every night.

96
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:32,720
What are you doing?

97
00:09:35,279 --> 00:09:36,120
Madam Gu just woke up.

98
00:09:37,039 --> 00:09:39,159
I am adjusting the bed position for her.

99
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:43,799
Mu Shaoze,

100
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:45,399
she is my wife.

101
00:09:46,039 --> 00:09:47,000
Your sister-in-law.

102
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:48,320
I'm not your wife.

103
00:09:48,559 --> 00:09:50,399
I don't have a husband
who would abandon me.

104
00:09:59,279 --> 00:09:59,919
I know.

105
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:01,720
Mom and Jinxi

106
00:10:01,879 --> 00:10:03,320
have gone too far this time.

107
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:03,960
Too far?

108
00:10:04,679 --> 00:10:06,960
Not an apology from them so far.

109
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:10,519
Then let me apologize for them.

110
00:10:10,639 --> 00:10:11,279
No need.

111
00:10:11,759 --> 00:10:13,320
I will not have any contact
with your family.

112
00:10:13,919 --> 00:10:14,679
I will not go back.

113
00:10:15,639 --> 00:10:16,480
Please leave.

114
00:10:17,720 --> 00:10:20,559
Mr. He, please consider
the patient's feelings.

115
00:10:25,519 --> 00:10:25,960
Fine.

116
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:27,600
Fine.

117
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:43,879
I am done with being the pushover wife

118
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:45,320
in this rich family.

119
00:10:46,159 --> 00:10:46,679
Good.

120
00:10:47,600 --> 00:10:49,639
I don't want you to be caught up
in this mess either.

121
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:51,440
I was curious before

122
00:10:51,759 --> 00:10:53,120
why you were faking Gu Qingmei.

123
00:10:54,639 --> 00:10:55,399
Now it seems

124
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:57,399
it was just a coincidence.

125
00:10:58,360 --> 00:10:59,799
I am just as confused as you are.

126
00:11:00,279 --> 00:11:02,519
Where on earth did Gu Qingmei go?

127
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:05,240
I am stuck here suffering for her.

128
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:07,360
Anyway, I am not going back

129
00:11:07,480 --> 00:11:08,320
to the He family.

130
00:11:10,240 --> 00:11:10,919
Don't worry.

131
00:11:11,679 --> 00:11:12,600
From now on,

132
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:14,679
I will not let the He family hurt you.

133
00:11:38,279 --> 00:11:38,720
Hello.

134
00:11:39,080 --> 00:11:39,840
Hello, boss.

135
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:41,799
Tian Gang was almost killed tonight.

136
00:11:42,279 --> 00:11:43,799
Luckily, our people found him in time.

137
00:11:45,879 --> 00:11:46,559
Tian Gang.

138
00:11:51,559 --> 00:11:52,679
Who... who's that?

139
00:11:54,240 --> 00:11:54,799
Please don't kill me!

140
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:55,799
You can speak.

141
00:11:55,919 --> 00:11:56,600
Please don't kill me!

142
00:11:57,480 --> 00:11:58,759
What is it that you know

143
00:11:59,120 --> 00:12:00,240
that they want you dead?

144
00:12:02,159 --> 00:12:02,840
I don't know.

145
00:12:03,919 --> 00:12:04,600
I don't know.

146
00:12:04,639 --> 00:12:06,519
You got lucky this time.

147
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:07,960
Next time, you won't be so lucky.

148
00:12:10,919 --> 00:12:11,879
To tell you the truth,

149
00:12:12,320 --> 00:12:13,120
I am not Gu Qingmei.

150
00:12:13,240 --> 00:12:14,480
I just look like her.

151
00:12:14,919 --> 00:12:15,720
I am a journalist.

152
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:18,080
I am also investigating the secrets
behind Meiyan International.

153
00:12:19,639 --> 00:12:20,559
Can we talk now?

154
00:12:21,480 --> 00:12:22,240
Alright, alright.

155
00:12:23,039 --> 00:12:23,679
I will tell you.

156
00:12:26,399 --> 00:12:28,240
Though the data I gave you were forged,

157
00:12:28,519 --> 00:12:29,519
the ingredients of the drug

158
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:31,600
do contain prohibited substances.

159
00:12:33,960 --> 00:12:35,639
I think I remember its code name.

160
00:12:36,360 --> 00:12:37,919
TAF990.

161
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:41,360
It is a prohibited active substance

162
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:43,399
that damages human skin.

163
00:12:44,039 --> 00:12:45,799
Routine tests cannot detect it.

164
00:12:46,320 --> 00:12:47,559
TAF990.

165
00:12:47,799 --> 00:12:48,559
How do you know?

166
00:12:48,960 --> 00:12:50,600
A friend of mine was the QA director.

167
00:12:52,759 --> 00:12:54,639
He told us once when he was drunk.

168
00:12:55,440 --> 00:12:56,120
Later,

169
00:12:57,559 --> 00:12:59,000
he died in an accident.

170
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:02,519
People in our department
were also fired one by one.

171
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:05,519
Think about it.

172
00:13:06,679 --> 00:13:08,080
We all lost our jobs

173
00:13:09,039 --> 00:13:11,679
and did not receive any compensation.

174
00:13:14,600 --> 00:13:16,240
I strongly suspect my buddy

175
00:13:17,039 --> 00:13:18,279
was murdered.

176
00:13:20,320 --> 00:13:21,480
I want to expose Meiyan.

177
00:13:23,039 --> 00:13:24,519
I want to avenge my friend!

178
00:13:33,279 --> 00:13:34,840
But I am also scared.

179
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:39,639
Please help us!

180
00:13:46,960 --> 00:13:47,559
Dad,

181
00:13:47,919 --> 00:13:48,879
look what she has done to

182
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:50,200
Mom and me!

183
00:13:50,840 --> 00:13:51,600
Shut up!

184
00:13:52,519 --> 00:13:53,480
Your mother is to blame.

185
00:13:54,120 --> 00:13:56,159
She brought those scammers in.

186
00:13:56,559 --> 00:13:58,519
You have disgraced the He family.

187
00:13:59,120 --> 00:14:00,240
But she...

188
00:14:00,320 --> 00:14:00,840
Enough!

189
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:03,080
If you hadn't been stirring things up,

190
00:14:03,279 --> 00:14:04,960
none of this would have happened.

191
00:14:09,919 --> 00:14:10,919
Pack your things.

192
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:13,240
Tomorrow, you take Mom
to the Xishan Villa for some rest.

193
00:14:13,919 --> 00:14:14,879
What?

194
00:14:15,039 --> 00:14:15,919
Without my call,

195
00:14:16,519 --> 00:14:17,240
don't come back.

196
00:14:17,759 --> 00:14:18,440
That is good.

197
00:14:19,519 --> 00:14:20,240
When you get there,

198
00:14:20,639 --> 00:14:21,919
reflect on what you've done.

199
00:14:22,279 --> 00:14:23,320
I am not going!

200
00:14:23,919 --> 00:14:25,440
Why are you all taking her side?

201
00:14:25,799 --> 00:14:27,480
I am your family!

202
00:14:27,600 --> 00:14:28,519
If you keep making a scene,

203
00:14:29,159 --> 00:14:30,360
get out of the He family

204
00:14:30,720 --> 00:14:31,600
and never come back!

205
00:14:39,840 --> 00:14:41,360
Gu Qingmei!

206
00:15:03,300 --> 00:15:08,060
♪Time stole the proof of our love♪

207
00:15:08,060 --> 00:15:12,900
♪Hidden in the moonlight,
lost in the clouds♪

208
00:15:12,900 --> 00:15:17,460
♪Tangled glances and love fall together♪

209
00:15:17,460 --> 00:15:22,380
♪Into a spiral of thoughts,
memories rewinding♪

210
00:15:22,380 --> 00:15:26,180
♪Feelings both strange and familiar♪

211
00:15:26,180 --> 00:15:30,980
♪I just know you're
where my heart belongs♪

212
00:15:30,980 --> 00:15:33,820
♪Can't remember
when this flutter started♪

213
00:15:33,820 --> 00:15:36,500
♪Or how it's supposed to end♪

214
00:15:36,860 --> 00:15:42,420
♪Goodbye to the world rushing in♪

215
00:15:42,820 --> 00:15:49,620
♪Let me hide in your eyes
and never leave♪

216
00:15:49,900 --> 00:15:54,580
♪Feel the rhythm of your heartbeat♪

217
00:15:54,740 --> 00:16:01,540
♪Every tomorrow seems worth the wait♪

218
00:16:01,860 --> 00:16:08,660
♪Let me fill the emptiness of a century♪

219
00:16:08,860 --> 00:16:13,340
♪As the wind brushes past your hem♪

220
00:16:13,340 --> 00:16:16,700
♪All my hidden feelings come undone♪

221
00:16:16,700 --> 00:16:23,620
♪Right as I confess my love♪
